Class CDBabySalesDataCrawler

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class CDBabySalesDataCrawler
extends java.lang.Thread
    This is the web crawler implementation class for crawling the CDBaby site and downloading sales information. It is instantiated and called by the CDBabySalesDataCrawlerUI class
    Author:
    jonlareau, Willful Wreckords, LLC, willfulwreckords@gmail.com

      • parseArgs

        public void parseArgs(java.lang.String[] args)

        Accepted arguments

        required [-username | -u] string string = The CD Baby Account username to use
        required [-password | -p] string string = The CD Baby Account Password to use
        required -outdir string string = The output directory to place completed files
        optional -dohtml [true|false]
        optional -doxml [true|false]
        optional -docsv [true|false]
        optional -doxlsx [true|false]
        optional -doftp [true|false]
        optional -ftpusername string string = The FTP username to use
        optional -ftppassword string string = The FTP password to use
        optional -ftpserver string string = The FTP server url to use
        optional -ftpport string string = The FTP port to use
        optional -ftpdirectory string string = The FTP directory to use
        optional -driver [(firefox) | chrome | safari | ie] string = The WEBDriver to use to use
        optional -sheeetitle string string = The Title of the xlsx sheet to use
        optional -startpage string string = The url of the CDBaby login page
        optional -clickdelay string string = The amount of click delay to use
        optional -h Print help information
        Parameters:
        args -
